[Student "S"]
{You dealt this hand.  

You decide to preempt 3\S with this hand. Partner's eyes wobble and he jumps straight to 4NT.  

With 1 Ace and a void in a lower-ranking suit you should bid 6 of that suit. So you bid 6\C. Partner jumps again, this time to 7\S. What do you b . . . oh never mind.}

